citations:
  citation-awoiaf-galbart-glover:
    source: source-awoiaf
    properties:
      locator: "Galbart Glover"
      accessed: "2026-03-15"
    notes: "Northmen culture. Born at Deepwood Motte. House Glover. Title: Master of Deepwood Motte. Unwed. Ward: Larence Snow (bastard of Hornwood). Loyal bannerman of House Stark who marched south with Robb Stark. Sent by Robb with Maege Mormont to sail up the Neck and contact Howland Reed, carrying Robb's will."
